### valid CCA2 Country Code in JPA Repository
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/postalcodes/NL

### invalid CCA2 country code > three characters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/postalcodes/NLD

### invalid CCA2 country code > letters and digits
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/postalcodes/N1

### valid CCA2 Country Code not in JPA Repository
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/postalcodes/IT

### valid CCA2 Country Code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/postalcodes/IT

### valid CCA2 Country Code
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/postalcodes/GR